Installation 
============

Installation from github
------------------------

	cd build/
	cmake .. -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release 
	make
	ctest  # test execution
	make install

In order to debug, it can be build with CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug.
The library will then send its debug information to STDERR.

Documentation
-------------

In order to generate documentation:
	cd build/
	cmake .. -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release 
	make doc

The generated doxygen files will be inside build/doxygen-doc/
